# Workspace — paths and artifact routing

Resolver source: `spa/paths.py`. Env overrides: `SPA_DATA_DIR`, `SPA_AUDIT_DIR`.

## Default paths (no env override)

| Resolver | Path |
|----------|------|
| `get_drafts_dir()` | `workspace/.data/drafts/` |
| `get_proposals_dir()` | `workspace/proposals/` |

Hermes MCP mounts `workspace/drafts/` (not `.data`). Skill default output is `.data/drafts/` — check both or pass `--output-dir workspace/drafts/<skill>`.

## inbox/ → process pipeline

```
inbox/<descriptive-name>.md
  └─► spa ingest inbox/<file>
        → memory (redacted)
        → meeting-synth → workspace/.data/drafts/meeting-synth/
        → tickets     → workspace/proposals/tickets/
        → policy      → workspace/proposals/03-policies/proposals/
```

Meeting auto-detect: ≥2 of `decisions`, `action items`, `risks`, `transcript`, `meeting`, `attendees`.

## Artifact naming

```
# Skill JSON (spa run-skill default)
workspace/.data/drafts/<skill>/<skill>-<YYYYMMDDTHHMMSSZ>.json

# AI-Proposed tickets (A2)
workspace/proposals/tickets/ticket-proposal-<ticket-id>.json
# Required: status=ai_proposed, assignee=unassigned

# Policy redline staging
workspace/proposals/03-policies/proposals/<policy-slug>-redline.md
workspace/proposals/draft-pr-body-<policy-slug>.md

# Daily brief
workspace/proposals/daily-brief-<YYYYMMDD>.md
```

## When editing here

| Action | Do |
|--------|-----|
| New raw input | Write to `inbox/`, then `spa ingest` |
| Meeting / ticket / policy output | Run `spa run-skill` — don't mimic verifier output by hand |
| Review tickets | Keep `assignee: unassigned`; assignment needs CPO (A3) |
| Promote policy redline | Move to `brain/03-policies/proposals/` after review |
| Promote evidence | Move index to `brain/evidence/<CC-slug>/` |

## Explicit skill run

```bash
source .venv/bin/activate
spa run-skill meeting-synth --input inbox/notes.md
spa run-skill ticket-draft --input path/to/issue.md
spa run-skill policy-redline --input path/to/change.md
```

Fixtures for input shape: `evals/fixtures/`.
